{"tid":1398044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全世界入］基本法明確寫明香港人有罷工權利","createTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T05:38:22.000Z","uid":18577,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"978ff7d42d053c20ce25d4f76bcbd7cbab8efb99","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"由琴日開始個班牛鬼蛇神係咁譴責恐嚇香港人千其唔好罷工<br />\n講到罷一日工就去返石器時代乜乜乜..真係人唔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我可以好肯定話你知叫你唔好罷工嘅一定係外國勢力係鬼<br />\n<br />\n因為大家睇下基本法第三章二十七條<br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。 <br />\n<br />\n所以個班話唔可以罷工嘅完全係衝突緊基本法<br />\n<br />\n連登身為香港第一大愛國愛港嘅討論區<br />\n對於基本法我相信連登上下都係真誠擁護<br />\n<br />\n所以我係道呼籲連登上下8月5號一齊參與三罷行動<br />\n體現香港基本法富予大家嘅權利<br />\n亦都能夠體現香港五十年不變一國兩制港人治港嘅方針<br />\n<br />\n愛國愛港嘅你無理由唔罷工<br />\n用行動去愛國愛港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jfj4Ne0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfj4Ne0.png&h=5c27885d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxVjA8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxVjA8k.png&h=4adb32b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYRuYmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYRuYmO.png&h=ef186c51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XOdFz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XOdFz8.png&h=cb2b282a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6beee2aeaf677647fc21d17ad95510f52c1c69ec","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"補返條基本法link先<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/pda/tc/basiclawtext/chapter_3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.basiclaw.gov.hk%2Fpda%2Ftc%2Fbasiclawtext%2Fchapter_3.html&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDQKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=a193ef18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.basiclaw.gov.hk/pda/tc/basiclawtext/chapter_3.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以大大聲聲同反對罷工嘅人講<br />\n<br />\n你依家係咪唔認基本法<br />\n係咪想搞港獨<br />\n基本法寫明我有罷工自由"},{"pid":"9b7ff248ed716f407de9db66f45107bdbef29651","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5403009635418079690006aeeec15029feac3872","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c619a6d7b19144ded704942c48c86c6a5e75c64c","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8409e264b6a1ca4c66f54e5f3738dd5cf825fae","tid":1398044,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ff24b824244a2a956e2020d7d5b2bd788d6e2a8","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8409e264b6a1ca4c66f54e5f3738dd5cf825fae","tid":1398044,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"對住藍絲大家記住問佢你係咪想反政府<br />\n係政府基本法寫明我可以有罷工自由"},{"pid":"f9d343feae07ee5b4f882fa4f5d197aa7f4ae94b","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"我愛基本法<br />\n罷工有辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e467e5f30b4e27c26e81852a1999100e9fefdf9a","tid":1398044,"uid":172092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"201