efb99","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"由琴日開始個班牛鬼蛇神係咁譴責恐嚇香港人千其唔好罷工<br />\n講到罷一日工就去返石器時代乜乜乜..真係人唔笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我可以好肯定話你知叫你唔好罷工嘅一定係外國勢力係鬼<br />\n<br />\n因為大家睇下基本法第三章二十七條<br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。 <br />\n<br />\n所以個班話唔可以罷工嘅完全係衝突緊基本法<br />\n<br />\n連登身為香港第一大愛國愛港嘅討論區<br />\n對於基本法我相信連登上下都係真誠擁護<br />\n<br />\n所以我係道呼籲連登上下8月5號一齊參與三罷行動<br />\n體現香港基本法富予大家嘅權利<br />\n亦都能夠體現香港五十年不變一國兩制港人治港嘅方針<br />\n<br />\n愛國愛港嘅你無理由唔罷工<br />\n用行動去愛國愛港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jfj4Ne0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJfj4Ne0.png&h=5c27885d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxVjA8k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxVjA8k.png&h=4adb32b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KYRuYmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKYRuYmO.png&h=ef186c51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XOdFz8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XOdFz8.png&h=cb2b282a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"人大釋法，可以追溯，罷工既就打靶！"},{"pid":"1b66909dec0520004c2fcd320c9a11af136ad252","tid":1398044,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"如果有人重推按基本法27條，恢復集體談判權，就唔使咁難推罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c4cad325b2bb0f4d2486a329ca0f241808f608","tid":1398044,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1640957140a3fc51dec00af995f43a92e9e099d","tid":1398044,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"基本法夠有廿二條啦<br />\n嚟到今日以為嗰頁俾人撕左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"我唔理<br />\n依刻我要用廿七條去罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sup